Dear Hiring Team,

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Engineer* role with *Chalk*. I bring over three years of professional experience building production-grade backend systems, distributed data infrastructure, and query-planning-inspired execution layers, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

