I have always been passionate about eliminating complexity and latency barriers that constrain ML capabilities, and delivering intuitive, powerful data infrastructure that integrates seamlessly with developers' favorite tools. I envision myself contributing to Chalk's mission of powering real-time machine learning decisions that transform industries — from stopping fraudulent credit card swipes to maximizing clean energy capture. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

